    "description": "Experience a non-linear turn-based horror RPG. Navigate through eerie corridors and surreal dimensions, while battling and evading terrifying monsters. Grow stronger by exploring every corner, not grinding battles. Forge your own path to vibrant colorful worlds, and decide the fate of the universe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Engaging Overworld, Battle or Escape!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/93e0944cd694d025d3a723d2c32a862a.poster.avif?t=1764619639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/93e0944cd694d025d3a723d2c32a862a.webm?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/93e0944cd694d025d3a723d2c32a862a.mp4?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Navigating the overworld is very dynamic! Hit enemies with your bat, avoid traps, stealth by enemies, and fight big bosses with multiple phases in the overworld as well as in the combat screen!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exploration Focused, No Grind!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/5effb7f813c299baacf4165c346fe4a6.poster.avif?t=1764619639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/5effb7f813c299baacf4165c346fe4a6.webm?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/5effb7f813c299baacf4165c346fe4a6.mp4?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Go where you want, only gated by various ability unlocks. You also get stronger from exploring to find equipment, experience points, and pets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fierce Enemies, In and Out of Combat!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/49d1a0920f658ccf17953cd58b066734.poster.avif?t=1764619639\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/49d1a0920f658ccf17953cd58b066734.webm?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/49d1a0920f658ccf17953cd58b066734.mp4?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/4f7a98a203a3e564ea259cba966a8b5a.poster.avif?t=1764619639\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/4f7a98a203a3e564ea259cba966a8b5a.webm?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/4f7a98a203a3e564ea259cba966a8b5a.mp4?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gain advantages through gameplay elements in the overworld and avoid dangerous enemies to survive. Enemies have their own particular behaviors in and out of combat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deep Customization, Equipment, Companions, and Pets!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/203cfc9afee065a9d7c578297982a2d6.poster.avif?t=1764619639\" width=598 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/203cfc9afee065a9d7c578297982a2d6.webm?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135540/extras/203cfc9afee065a9d7c578297982a2d6.mp4?t=1764619639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Items you discover grant unique abilities in battle, allowing for flexible customization. Companions and pets each have a special battle mechanic that modifies how combat plays out.",
